WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
â™ªThat dayâ™ª

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
â™ªNothing stays together foreverâ™ª

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
â™ªI've quit romanceâ™ª

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
â™ªWho hasn't failed againâ™ª

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
â™ªCrying in deathâ™ª

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
â™ªAnd in lifeâ™ª

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
â™ªEven nowâ™ª

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
â™ªWe keep learningâ™ª

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
â™ªIt's no surpriseâ™ª

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
â™ªBeing happy is so hardâ™ª

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
â™ªWeirdly, I became a role modelâ™ª

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
â™ªOn the day we met again, we said hiâ™ª

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
â™ªIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaintâ™ª

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
â™ªWho can do anything without regretâ™ª

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
â™ªI am all rightâ™ª

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
â™ªMay you live in peaceâ™ª

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
â™ªLet the world roarâ™ª

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
â™ªSounds like a carnivalâ™ª

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
â™ªBeing alive is never dullâ™ª

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
â™ªHow wonderful to be freeâ™ª

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
â™ªI became even better without youâ™ª

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
â™ªNothing can be perfectâ™ª

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
â™ªWe bless each other in painâ™ª

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
â™ªWe nod and smileâ™ª

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
â™ªMay we both be wellâ™ª

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.104 --> 01:43.992
=Episode 9=

01:44.413 --> 01:45.333
First, let's turn to

01:45.333 --> 01:46.853
the latest on global markets.

01:47.452 --> 01:49.773
(Host, Xu Yan)
Renewed confidence

01:49.853 --> 01:51.732
fueled a global market rally yesterday.

01:52.053 --> 01:53.853
(Nasdaq hits all-time high)
The Nasdaq index,

01:53.892 --> 01:55.372
fueled by tech giants,

01:55.413 --> 01:56.853
has surged to a new record high,

01:57.133 --> 01:58.693
climbing over 1 percent.

02:00.333 --> 02:01.053
I think

02:01.613 --> 02:03.812
delivering it in a steadier pace

02:04.053 --> 02:04.532
is better.

02:04.812 --> 02:05.773
I don't agree.

02:06.252 --> 02:07.053
I think it's great.

02:09.173 --> 02:09.733
Moreover,

02:09.773 --> 02:10.773
this suits her better

02:10.812 --> 02:12.053
than food programs.

02:17.412 --> 02:17.893
Yan.

02:22.933 --> 02:23.972
A surprise for you.

02:25.613 --> 02:26.493
Want to know?

02:30.412 --> 02:31.252
We two

02:31.333 --> 02:32.453
have been thinking about

02:35.092 --> 02:36.453
giving you a special gift.

02:36.624 --> 02:37.072
Here.

02:37.173 --> 02:38.293
Congratulations!

02:38.812 --> 02:40.613
Thank you, Mom, Dad.

02:41.293 --> 02:42.053
Open it and check.

02:46.572 --> 02:47.692
This is too expensive.

02:48.213 --> 02:48.933
Do you like it?

02:50.092 --> 02:50.933
I'm glad you like it.

02:53.013 --> 02:53.812
Thank you.

02:58.733 --> 03:00.293
Both of us think

03:00.412 --> 03:02.213
now that you're an anchor,

03:02.692 --> 03:03.652
your on-screen presence

03:03.773 --> 03:05.053
should be more elegant.

03:05.293 --> 03:06.252
Rubies are perfect.

03:09.213 --> 03:10.333
Let me put them on you.

03:11.173 --> 03:12.572
You're always thoughtful.

03:13.213 --> 03:14.493
I'd only know

03:14.532 --> 03:15.173
to buy bags,

03:15.613 --> 03:16.773
which are useless here.

03:17.652 --> 03:18.652
If you think in this way,

03:18.933 --> 03:19.933
you must strive to

03:19.972 --> 03:22.013
keep your wife satisfied.

03:23.252 --> 03:23.733
Right?

03:23.952 --> 03:24.372
Right.

03:24.652 --> 03:25.173
Haoming.

03:26.132 --> 03:26.532
Haoming.

03:26.893 --> 03:28.272
I'll switch horses next Saturday.

03:28.272 --> 03:29.264
Can you go with me?

03:30.053 --> 03:30.613
Saturday?

03:31.053 --> 03:31.812
Not Saturday.

03:32.173 --> 03:32.933
He and I

03:32.972 --> 03:34.053
have a meeting with Mr. Wu.

03:34.652 --> 03:35.132
Fine.

03:37.333 --> 03:38.412
I'm not important.

03:40.372 --> 03:40.852
Haochen.

03:43.652 --> 03:44.572
Maybe I'll go with you.

03:44.972 --> 03:46.333
Do you know about horse switching?

03:46.692 --> 03:47.453
This kid...

03:48.532 --> 03:49.213
Alright.

03:51.213 --> 03:51.692
Forget it.

03:53.092 --> 03:54.412
Let me try these earrings on you.

03:57.572 --> 03:58.013
Catch!

03:58.173 --> 03:58.692
Go!

03:58.692 --> 03:59.092
Pass it!

04:04.933 --> 04:06.213
- Stop fighting!
- Stop!

04:06.412 --> 04:07.213
Stop it!

04:07.372 --> 04:07.972
Bu!

04:09.412 --> 04:10.412
Throw it farther.

04:12.493 --> 04:13.053
Bu.

04:13.372 --> 04:13.893
Bu.

04:14.812 --> 04:15.333
Bu, come.

04:16.012 --> 04:16.372
Come.

04:17.372 --> 04:17.692
Come.

04:19.346 --> 04:19.933
(Parents' Group)

04:19.933 --> 04:21.053
What happened?

04:21.293 --> 04:22.252
So annoying.

04:22.293 --> 04:23.173
Ready, Bu?

04:24.853 --> 04:25.613
Trouble again.

04:25.653 --> 04:26.093
Mr. Wang.

04:30.533 --> 04:31.212
What's up, Mom?

04:31.933 --> 04:33.613
Haochen's teacher texted me.

04:34.053 --> 04:35.252
He hit a classmate again

04:35.293 --> 04:36.252
during P.E. class.

04:36.452 --> 04:37.493
Not his first offense.

04:37.892 --> 04:39.312
His parents insist me to go.

04:39.312 --> 04:40.272
I'm so busy!

04:40.733 --> 04:42.173
Hosting ten feasts

04:42.613 --> 04:43.692
is easier than dealing

04:43.733 --> 04:44.892
with his teacher's message.

04:45.332 --> 04:47.173
Haochen always causes trouble.

04:47.452 --> 04:48.252
I'd be lectured

04:48.252 --> 04:50.012
by these young teachers.

04:50.533 --> 04:51.892
We are all busy.

04:52.212 --> 04:52.812
And I have

04:53.012 --> 04:53.692
to handle these.

04:53.812 --> 04:55.533
I'm overwhelmed. This is annoying.

04:55.853 --> 04:57.173
Every time the teacher calls,

04:57.212 --> 04:58.053
my heart aches.

05:02.653 --> 05:03.973
You're more patient than I am.

05:05.212 --> 05:06.252
I'll add you to the group,

05:06.372 --> 05:07.093
and I'll exit.

05:08.053 --> 05:08.733
Deal then.

05:09.973 --> 05:10.692
Is it okay, Mom?

05:10.733 --> 05:11.533
It's perfectly okay.

05:11.853 --> 05:12.733
You married Haoming,

05:12.772 --> 05:13.653
and we are family now.

05:13.733 --> 05:15.173
You are also Haochen's guardian.

05:15.653 --> 05:16.293
Deal then.

05:16.572 --> 05:17.572
I'll tell his teacher.

05:19.692 --> 05:20.212
Okay.

05:23.452 --> 05:24.132
But, Mom.

05:24.853 --> 05:26.212
It's my first time being a parent.

05:26.293 --> 05:27.572
There's much I don't understand.

05:27.692 --> 05:28.653
Please guide me.

05:29.012 --> 05:30.653
No need. Just follow instructions.

05:30.733 --> 05:32.892
Apologize when needed. Alright.

05:33.613 --> 05:34.533
I've added you.

05:35.372 --> 05:35.812
(Parents' Group)
I'm in.

05:35.812 --> 05:39.812
(You've joined this group chat.)

05:39.812 --> 05:40.452
The teacher...

05:40.493 --> 05:41.173
Bu!

05:41.452 --> 05:41.973
Bu, come.

05:42.012 --> 05:42.892
I will play with you.

05:44.293 --> 05:44.733
Here.

05:45.212 --> 05:45.733
Babe.

05:46.533 --> 05:47.252
Come here. Come.

05:48.272 --> 05:49.232
(Haochen's parent,)
(Haochen's parent,)

05:49.776 --> 05:52.208
(Haochen got into another fight in P.E.)
(Haochen got into another fight in P.E.)

05:52.208 --> 05:53.424
(and hurt a classmate.)
(and hurt a classmate.)

05:53.933 --> 05:55.252
(The school's talked to him,)
(The school's talked to him,)

05:55.293 --> 05:56.272
(but it's useless.)
(but it's useless.)

05:56.688 --> 05:58.800
(The injured child's parents are furious,)
(The injured child's parents are furious,)

05:59.056 --> 06:00.656
(waiting in the office.)
(waiting in the office.)

06:00.656 --> 06:02.128
(Come to the school now.)
(Come to the school now.)

06:04.973 --> 06:06.093
Understood.

06:06.332 --> 06:08.812
I'll talk to him when we get home.

06:08.892 --> 06:10.252
Sorry, we'll take the blame.

06:11.093 --> 06:13.012
When you get home, talk it out with him.

06:13.372 --> 06:14.093
As his family,

06:14.132 --> 06:15.812
you can't just dump him at school

06:15.933 --> 06:17.012
and leave him alone.

06:17.293 --> 06:19.093
This doesn't work.

06:19.533 --> 06:20.533
Understood.

06:20.933 --> 06:21.812
After we go back,

06:21.853 --> 06:23.053
I'll talk to him.

06:23.293 --> 06:23.772
Alright.

06:24.012 --> 06:24.653
That's it.

06:24.933 --> 06:25.572
Thank you.

06:26.053 --> 06:26.480
Goodbye.

06:36.173 --> 06:36.533
Okay.

06:37.132 --> 06:37.653
Next one.

06:39.372 --> 06:40.452
Move to the center.

06:42.132 --> 06:42.653
Next one.

07:02.572 --> 07:03.533
Want to tell me

07:03.533 --> 07:04.892
what happened today?

07:12.252 --> 07:13.252
Don't worry.

07:14.252 --> 07:15.053
The kid's parents

07:15.093 --> 07:16.533
won't pursue it further.

07:17.173 --> 07:18.173
But I think

07:19.332 --> 07:20.653
we need to talk it out.

07:27.533 --> 07:28.692
Can you hear me?

07:41.533 --> 07:42.012
Back?

07:44.613 --> 07:45.772
Yan, how was it?

07:46.653 --> 07:49.012
The kid's parents
won't pursue it further.

07:51.933 --> 07:54.053
He really needs to control his temper.

07:54.053 --> 07:54.973
He's only twelve.

07:55.332 --> 07:56.080
When he's older,

07:56.208 --> 07:57.136
we can't control him.

07:57.853 --> 07:59.452
What we're providing him with

07:59.493 --> 08:00.853
the best educational resources.

08:00.892 --> 08:01.812
An excellent school.

08:02.212 --> 08:02.653
Right?

08:03.173 --> 08:04.332
Now we need

08:04.413 --> 08:05.212
to focus on

08:05.572 --> 08:07.533
solving the problem.

08:09.173 --> 08:10.772
Maybe we should consider

08:11.093 --> 08:12.093
sending him abroad.

08:17.053 --> 08:17.493
Mom.

08:18.533 --> 08:19.772
Haochen is only twelve.

08:20.252 --> 08:21.613
Isn't it too early for him?

08:22.093 --> 08:23.053
Ms. Sun's child

08:23.093 --> 08:24.452
went abroad even younger than him.

08:24.812 --> 08:25.933
Went to Australia at eight.

08:26.173 --> 08:27.933
Wait, this varies case by case.

08:28.132 --> 08:29.332
He just turned twelve.

08:29.372 --> 08:30.413
If we send him abroad now,

08:30.533 --> 08:31.493
he might

08:31.533 --> 08:32.373
go astray,

08:32.492 --> 08:33.612
and no one will

08:33.653 --> 08:34.572
correct him then.

08:34.572 --> 08:35.893
But he's a boy.

08:36.253 --> 08:37.253
He could benefit from it.

08:37.293 --> 08:38.533
I don't oppose it.

08:38.612 --> 08:39.492
But we must

08:39.612 --> 08:40.612
find the right timing.

08:40.972 --> 08:41.893
It varies case by case.

08:42.092 --> 08:43.053
Maybe it works

08:43.173 --> 08:44.053
for other kids,

08:44.092 --> 08:44.812
but not ours.

08:44.893 --> 08:46.933
Listen, he's been spoiled...

08:55.612 --> 08:57.212
The school isn't over yet.

08:59.092 --> 08:59.773
I'll go check.

09:10.253 --> 09:11.092
I think we should

09:11.133 --> 09:12.253
discuss this with him.

09:13.253 --> 09:14.612
Let's hear what Haochen thinks.

09:15.413 --> 09:16.332
If he rejects,

09:16.373 --> 09:17.013
don't force him.

09:17.612 --> 09:18.013
Haoming.

09:18.972 --> 09:19.893
In this entire family,

09:20.332 --> 09:21.373
you spoil him the most.

09:21.812 --> 09:22.653
You take the blame

09:22.812 --> 09:23.812
for turning him this way.

09:25.133 --> 09:26.173
Reflect on this.

09:33.173 --> 09:33.773
Haochen.

09:44.013 --> 09:45.092
I think

09:45.133 --> 09:47.013
the school isn't over yet.

09:47.452 --> 09:47.972
Why you...?

09:48.013 --> 09:48.773
Let me ask you.

09:50.972 --> 09:52.492
Did you tell my parents

09:52.533 --> 09:53.732
to send me abroad?

09:56.732 --> 09:57.812
Why would I do that?

10:00.053 --> 10:01.653
Stop pretending.

10:02.013 --> 10:04.173
You made my brother fall for you,

10:04.373 --> 10:05.612
and then pleased my parents,

10:05.933 --> 10:07.212
until everyone adored you.

10:07.732 --> 10:09.452
But I didn't fall for your tricks.

10:09.732 --> 10:10.852
Now trying to drive me away?

10:10.893 --> 10:11.972
- Right?
- Right.

10:15.413 --> 10:16.852
You guessed it right.

10:18.332 --> 10:20.293
I do want to drive you away.

10:20.653 --> 10:21.413
And then

10:21.452 --> 10:22.572
make them all adore me.

10:23.533 --> 10:24.373
How clever of me!

10:26.053 --> 10:26.612
Shen Haochen.

10:27.173 --> 10:28.692
Use that little brain of yours.

10:29.133 --> 10:30.133
Does this make any sense?

10:32.253 --> 10:32.933
Let me tell you.

10:32.972 --> 10:34.212
I'm not going abroad.

10:34.332 --> 10:35.812
No matter what tricks you pull,

10:36.013 --> 10:36.972
I, Shen Haochen,

10:37.253 --> 10:38.212
fight you to the end.

10:38.253 --> 10:39.092
I don't know why

10:39.133 --> 10:40.293
you're so hostile toward me,

10:40.893 --> 10:41.773
but let me remind you,

10:42.253 --> 10:43.413
I married your brother.

10:43.452 --> 10:45.293
I'm your sister-in-law,
and we're family now.

10:45.933 --> 10:46.933
I love you

10:47.092 --> 10:48.013
how much they love you.

10:48.133 --> 10:49.173
I won't hurt you,

10:49.812 --> 10:50.572
so I don't need

10:50.612 --> 10:51.413
to send you abroad.

10:51.893 --> 10:53.092
Before you came,

10:53.212 --> 10:54.812
my brother spent every day with me.

11:03.732 --> 11:05.253
If you listen to me,

11:06.373 --> 11:07.133
and no more

11:07.253 --> 11:08.492
of today's incident,

11:09.413 --> 11:10.173
I can make

11:10.852 --> 11:12.173
Haoming spend more time with you.

11:13.373 --> 11:13.972
I can guarantee

11:15.173 --> 11:16.053
you would stay.

11:16.972 --> 11:17.572
Deal?

11:19.452 --> 11:20.773
What's this new trick?

11:26.653 --> 11:29.692
We're in an advantageous position.

11:30.492 --> 11:31.092
Have some tea.

11:34.972 --> 11:36.293
What does this mean?

11:36.812 --> 11:38.293
Jinda Group has agreed

11:38.492 --> 11:39.972
to grant us exclusive coverage

11:40.173 --> 11:42.332
of the New District development project.

11:43.173 --> 11:45.013
This is an extraordinary opportunity!

11:45.852 --> 11:47.893
Many media outlets are vying for this.

11:48.293 --> 11:50.092
And you're the perfect candidate
for this.

11:53.533 --> 11:54.413
I'm telling you.

11:55.092 --> 11:56.212
Once this project launches,

11:56.812 --> 11:58.413
it'll boost your career.

12:01.492 --> 12:01.893
Of course,

12:02.572 --> 12:04.133
your professional skills are excellent.

12:04.692 --> 12:06.053
But this will

12:06.373 --> 12:07.612
be the icing on the cake.

12:09.492 --> 12:10.133
Thank you, Sir.

12:10.572 --> 12:11.452
Not at all.

12:11.692 --> 12:12.612
Come on. Have some tea.

12:18.773 --> 12:19.344
Yan.

12:22.692 --> 12:23.692
There's a Mr. Zhou

12:23.732 --> 12:25.332
waiting for you downstairs.

12:28.972 --> 12:29.572
Okay.

12:33.893 --> 12:35.293
It's been so long.

12:35.452 --> 12:37.933
Five or six years, I think?

12:38.933 --> 12:39.568
How are you?

12:41.373 --> 12:42.053
Not bad.

12:43.053 --> 12:44.173
Seeing you on TV

12:44.452 --> 12:45.812
after all these years,

12:46.173 --> 12:47.253
you've fulfilled your dream

12:47.293 --> 12:48.452
of becoming a news anchor.

12:48.812 --> 12:49.692
I'm happy for you.

12:50.612 --> 12:51.053
Thank you.

12:55.893 --> 12:56.692
Remember?

12:57.373 --> 12:58.293
Our first meeting

12:58.332 --> 12:59.253
was also in a cafe.

13:01.136 --> 13:01.852
(Five Years Ago)

13:01.852 --> 13:03.092
Zhou, your project

13:03.133 --> 13:05.133
is too theoretical for me.

13:05.653 --> 13:06.173
Mr. Chen,

13:06.373 --> 13:07.253
there are

13:07.253 --> 13:07.972
very few experts

13:08.048 --> 13:09.136
involved in this research

13:09.136 --> 13:10.533
and not many people understand

13:10.612 --> 13:11.452
its systems.

13:11.812 --> 13:13.332
I believe in the upcoming future,

13:13.373 --> 13:14.092
it will become

13:14.133 --> 13:15.653
the prevailing trend in healthcare

13:15.893 --> 13:18.133
and empower doctors
to better serve patients.

13:18.293 --> 13:18.812
Alright.

13:19.173 --> 13:20.533
I understand your point.

13:21.013 --> 13:22.173
Let's stop here for today.

13:22.373 --> 13:23.253
I have a meeting soon.

13:23.492 --> 13:24.773
I'll consider it.

13:25.293 --> 13:25.893
Fine.

13:26.053 --> 13:26.852
Call me.

13:29.692 --> 13:30.212
Mr. Chen,

13:30.452 --> 13:31.212
the proposal.

13:31.293 --> 13:31.852
No need.

13:35.653 --> 13:36.253
Xu Yan.

13:37.852 --> 13:39.373
I've reviewed your resume, impressive.

13:40.373 --> 13:41.173
Finished the form?

13:41.972 --> 13:42.492
Yes.

13:42.572 --> 13:43.612
Here you go. Please.

13:48.533 --> 13:50.732
The family members
and occupations section

13:51.173 --> 13:52.092
is left blank here.

13:52.253 --> 13:53.133
Why?

14:01.373 --> 14:02.332
May I ask

14:03.492 --> 14:04.812
this section is mandatory?

14:05.413 --> 14:06.812
This top-tier media company

14:07.053 --> 14:09.013
puts great emphasis
on employees' backgrounds.

14:09.452 --> 14:11.133
Beyond education
and professional skills,

14:11.373 --> 14:12.533
family background serves as

14:12.893 --> 14:14.253
a part of background checks.

14:16.053 --> 14:16.653
Understood.

14:18.933 --> 14:20.773
I grew up with my grandma.

14:23.013 --> 14:23.612
Then I'll...

14:24.173 --> 14:25.212
May I ask

14:25.413 --> 14:26.692
about your parents' occupations?

14:30.893 --> 14:32.133
My family runs a barbershop.

14:33.533 --> 14:34.053
Include that?

14:34.092 --> 14:35.133
Then better not.

14:35.533 --> 14:37.492
This could get you a bonus,

14:37.533 --> 14:38.533
but filling it in

14:38.572 --> 14:39.373
will be unfavorable.

14:41.732 --> 14:42.933
But you can't leave it blank.

14:43.972 --> 14:45.133
Here's my suggestion.

14:45.492 --> 14:46.933
Overseas business operations.

14:47.373 --> 14:47.933
Don't worry.

14:48.053 --> 14:48.852
They usually

14:49.013 --> 14:50.053
can't verify this.

14:50.492 --> 14:51.212
It's safer.

14:51.492 --> 14:53.013
I advise you not to listen to her.

14:53.893 --> 14:54.653
Fabricating resumes

14:54.893 --> 14:56.653
is equivalent to planting

14:56.692 --> 14:58.133
a time bomb in your career.

14:58.173 --> 14:58.692
One day,

14:58.692 --> 14:59.773
it would suddenly explode.

15:00.212 --> 15:01.413
Then all your credibility

15:01.452 --> 15:02.653
and your previous efforts

15:02.692 --> 15:04.533
would be completely wasted.

15:04.972 --> 15:06.092
These despicable headhunters

15:06.133 --> 15:06.893
are increasing.

15:06.933 --> 15:08.972
What if they use this to threaten you?

15:09.013 --> 15:09.653
Nonsense.

15:11.013 --> 15:12.053
Miss.

15:12.173 --> 15:13.293
You're eavesdropping us,

15:13.692 --> 15:14.773
and now slandering me?

15:18.373 --> 15:19.332
Just fill it in here.

15:24.612 --> 15:25.533
- Here?
- Right.

15:27.536 --> 15:29.264
(Family Members)

15:39.732 --> 15:40.212
Miss.

15:41.013 --> 15:42.373
I just graduated.

15:42.933 --> 15:44.572
I want to be honest.

15:45.572 --> 15:46.653
If it's really

15:47.413 --> 15:48.533
as he said...

15:49.133 --> 15:49.933
Then I can't handle

15:49.972 --> 15:50.773
this case for you.

15:50.852 --> 15:51.332
Okay?

15:52.013 --> 15:53.173
I won't take the commission.

15:53.452 --> 15:54.492
- Miss.
- Can't believe it.

16:14.332 --> 16:14.893
Sorry.

16:14.972 --> 16:15.653
No problem.

16:16.972 --> 16:18.533
Hello. I'm Xu Yan.

16:19.053 --> 16:21.053
I submitted my resume to your company.

16:21.092 --> 16:22.293
Sorry, we're not interested.

16:22.413 --> 16:23.812
Wait. Please hear me out.

16:33.212 --> 16:33.692
For you.

16:36.933 --> 16:37.773
You failed today,

16:38.013 --> 16:39.133
but don't be discouraged.

16:39.413 --> 16:40.773
Just like this sunflower,

16:40.933 --> 16:42.533
thrive strongly and never give up.

16:45.732 --> 16:46.253
Thank you.

16:47.332 --> 16:47.812
Excuse me.

16:50.253 --> 16:50.653
Hello.

16:53.572 --> 16:54.013
Okay.

16:58.212 --> 16:58.852
Excuse me.

16:59.612 --> 17:00.692
Now I need one too.

17:01.933 --> 17:02.612
The investor

17:02.732 --> 17:03.173
won't come.

17:07.853 --> 17:08.252
Alright.

17:08.853 --> 17:09.532
Then let's

17:10.333 --> 17:11.373
thrive strongly together.

17:11.813 --> 17:12.413
Keep going!

17:15.772 --> 17:16.653
I-I want to ask

17:16.853 --> 17:17.573
if you made this

17:17.573 --> 17:18.813
from that proposal.

17:18.972 --> 17:19.452
Exactly.

17:19.492 --> 17:20.212
No one wants it.

17:20.613 --> 17:21.373
Need this resume?

17:21.532 --> 17:22.373
I can teach you.

17:22.413 --> 17:23.052
No, thanks.

17:25.093 --> 17:25.813
What's your name?

17:26.292 --> 17:26.972
I'm Zhou Zeyuan.

17:27.252 --> 17:27.692
And you?

17:28.052 --> 17:28.813
I'm Xu Yan.

17:29.052 --> 17:29.532
Xu Yan.

17:30.173 --> 17:31.452
Now you've become

17:31.532 --> 17:32.853
a genuinely successful woman.

17:34.292 --> 17:35.133
Not really.

17:36.012 --> 17:38.252
I just became a news anchor recently,

17:38.492 --> 17:40.173
still waiting to see audience feedback.

17:40.653 --> 17:41.933
It's too early to say so.

17:43.292 --> 17:44.212
Enough about me.

17:44.492 --> 17:45.732
What about you? What do you do?

17:47.173 --> 17:48.052
Those investors

17:48.093 --> 17:48.972
all doubted me,

17:49.052 --> 17:50.492
but I always believed in myself.

17:51.728 --> 17:53.933
When my company started,
there were only three.

17:53.933 --> 17:55.573
And now we have

17:55.613 --> 17:56.732
over 160 people

17:56.772 --> 17:57.424
in the company.

17:57.813 --> 17:59.052
We got three funding rounds,

17:59.413 --> 18:00.292
and expanded

18:00.333 --> 18:01.732
from domestic to overseas markets.

18:01.813 --> 18:02.732
We established branches

18:02.893 --> 18:03.972
in New York, London,

18:04.052 --> 18:04.893
and Ottawa.

18:05.373 --> 18:05.853
Mr. Zhou.

18:06.933 --> 18:09.212
And we signed a contract

18:09.252 --> 18:10.532
with a German institution.

18:10.613 --> 18:12.653
My plan is to collaborate with

18:12.653 --> 18:13.653
over 70 hospitals

18:13.692 --> 18:14.613
in three years.

18:14.613 --> 18:15.692
(He is radiant with vigor,)

18:15.893 --> 18:17.252
(and full of ambitious spirit,)

18:17.772 --> 18:18.853
(just like he was)

18:18.893 --> 18:19.772
(when we first met.)

18:20.692 --> 18:21.732
(The only difference)

18:22.292 --> 18:23.933
(might be his current outfit.)

18:24.933 --> 18:25.972
(It looks casual,)

18:26.413 --> 18:27.613
(without flashy logos,)

18:28.133 --> 18:29.972
(yet clearly expensive at first glance,)

18:30.653 --> 18:32.333
(perfectly embodying the image)

18:32.492 --> 18:33.772
(of a tech nouveau riche here.)

18:33.813 --> 18:35.133
Moreover, I plan

18:35.173 --> 18:36.373
to go public on NASDAQ

18:36.413 --> 18:37.452
by next year's end.

18:39.653 --> 18:41.052
- Have some water.
- Thanks.

18:42.133 --> 18:44.012
When we first met,

18:44.173 --> 18:46.252
we were all novices.

18:46.613 --> 18:48.012
Now look at us.

18:49.732 --> 18:51.813
I've believed
in the mysticism of persistence.

18:52.212 --> 18:53.452
Persistence will get rewards.

18:53.573 --> 18:55.333
We achieve what we're determined to do.

18:59.052 --> 18:59.613
Xu Yan,

19:00.133 --> 19:01.133
I know you married

19:01.173 --> 19:02.413
Shen Haoming from Jinda Group.

19:02.692 --> 19:04.012
Jinda Group is top-tier

19:04.052 --> 19:05.093
in the construction field.

19:05.492 --> 19:07.133
Their Investment Division

19:07.173 --> 19:08.573
is also highly reputable.

19:09.613 --> 19:10.692
Given our relationship,

19:11.093 --> 19:12.173
I'll be direct.

19:12.373 --> 19:13.373
To be honest,

19:14.333 --> 19:15.452
I came to you

19:15.492 --> 19:16.653
to connect through you

19:16.972 --> 19:17.772
with your husband.

19:18.413 --> 19:20.573
Collaborating with Jinda Group

19:20.772 --> 19:21.853
would benefit

19:22.093 --> 19:23.212
my company greatly.

19:29.212 --> 19:31.093
I deeply respect the industry

19:31.492 --> 19:32.732
and vision you've chosen.

19:34.893 --> 19:35.333
By the way,

19:35.933 --> 19:37.012
could you first send me

19:37.052 --> 19:38.732
your company's

19:38.853 --> 19:39.853
recent financial reports

19:39.893 --> 19:40.732
and business plans?

19:41.012 --> 19:42.212
Then I'll tell my husband.

19:43.093 --> 19:44.933
No problem. I'll prepare it right away.

19:45.853 --> 19:47.093
Thank you for your support.

19:47.573 --> 19:48.613
Not really.

19:49.292 --> 19:50.813
A worthwhile investment project

19:50.933 --> 19:52.613
can be beneficial, for my husband

19:53.333 --> 19:54.212
and the group.

19:54.653 --> 19:55.813
A win-win situation

19:56.972 --> 19:57.613
would be ideal.

20:00.452 --> 20:00.853
Mr. Zhou.

20:01.173 --> 20:02.333
Mr. Wang from Youkang Medical

20:02.452 --> 20:03.173
is here again.

20:03.813 --> 20:04.333
We agreed...

20:06.532 --> 20:07.012
Zhou.

20:08.012 --> 20:08.452
Zhou.

20:08.573 --> 20:09.732
I've tried to schedule you,

20:09.813 --> 20:10.772
but failed.

20:10.813 --> 20:12.560
Reserve this batch of equipment for me.

20:12.560 --> 20:13.456
The price is flexible.

20:13.456 --> 20:15.613
Let's sign the contract today.

20:15.653 --> 20:16.080
No, no.

20:16.452 --> 20:16.976
Wang.

20:16.976 --> 20:18.093
I've been so busy lately.

20:18.212 --> 20:19.813
And I have a guest here today.

20:20.212 --> 20:20.813
Another day.

20:21.052 --> 20:21.413
Fine.

20:21.732 --> 20:23.212
You go ahead. I'll wait here.

20:25.373 --> 20:25.972
Then sorry.

20:26.133 --> 20:26.813
Please wait here.

20:27.292 --> 20:28.653
Wang, come with me.

20:29.173 --> 20:31.012
Listen, I've tried to schedule you.

20:31.133 --> 20:32.252
I've been overwhelmed.

20:32.252 --> 20:32.732
Let's go.

20:35.312 --> 20:36.976
(New Medical Innovation Competition,
First Prize)

20:45.893 --> 20:46.532
Excuse me.

20:46.853 --> 20:47.692
Where's the restroom?

20:48.373 --> 20:49.452
Go straight and turn left.

20:49.653 --> 20:50.333
Okay, thank you.

20:58.893 --> 21:00.012
I haven't had my break yet.

21:00.893 --> 21:01.333
Yes.

21:01.653 --> 21:03.252
My current job is super easy.

21:03.732 --> 21:05.212
Just sit there doing nothing.

21:05.532 --> 21:06.452
Five hundred a day.

21:06.893 --> 21:08.252
Much easier than the filming work.

21:09.133 --> 21:09.933
Want to join me?

21:10.613 --> 21:11.732
Let's come together.

21:13.133 --> 21:14.573
Don't worry. No one notices you.

21:15.292 --> 21:16.532
Just sit at the desk

21:16.772 --> 21:17.692
and pretend to work.

21:19.452 --> 21:19.853
Exactly.

21:21.252 --> 21:22.573
It's just a shell company.

21:22.933 --> 21:23.813
Doesn't matter.

21:24.173 --> 21:25.252
They don't need skills.

21:38.653 --> 21:40.052
Can you show me?

21:43.972 --> 21:44.492
Of course.

21:46.532 --> 21:47.532
I-It's simple.

21:51.333 --> 21:52.133
Under maintenance.

21:52.173 --> 21:53.853
Let me find Mr. Wang
over in Engineering.

22:01.532 --> 22:02.292
Hello.

22:02.492 --> 22:05.173
This is Shangze Xinhui
Medical Technology.

22:06.252 --> 22:09.692
Hello. This is Shangze Xinhui
Medical Technology.

22:10.252 --> 22:12.012
We've completed

22:12.052 --> 22:13.813
comprehensive upgrades.

22:14.532 --> 22:15.972
Rest assured about our services.

22:16.413 --> 22:18.413
Our services are lifelong.

22:25.012 --> 22:26.492
For any problem,

22:26.532 --> 22:28.492
feel free to contact us anytime.

22:31.173 --> 22:31.613
Liang.

22:32.212 --> 22:33.452
About the financial report,

22:33.492 --> 22:34.492
the CFO wants to see you.

22:34.772 --> 22:35.413
What?

22:36.252 --> 22:37.452
A payment from the 15th

22:37.492 --> 22:38.413
needs verification.

22:38.452 --> 22:39.853
A payment on the 15th?

22:50.608 --> 22:52.976
(Sales Department Archives)

23:12.252 --> 23:12.772
Xu Yan.

23:15.613 --> 23:16.492
Sorry to let you wait.

23:16.813 --> 23:17.413
Mr. Wang left.

23:17.492 --> 23:18.573
Let's talk then.

23:21.012 --> 23:21.772
I didn't tell you

23:21.813 --> 23:22.772
I have plans tonight.

23:24.252 --> 23:24.692
It's okay.

23:25.532 --> 23:26.212
Call me.

23:26.373 --> 23:26.653
Okay.

24:02.292 --> 24:03.212
Honey, are you done?

24:03.692 --> 24:04.093
Almost.

24:10.972 --> 24:11.532
By the way,

24:12.093 --> 24:13.212
is cousin still in Jingzhou?

24:16.853 --> 24:17.653
Probably.

24:20.292 --> 24:21.052
She found a job?

24:24.173 --> 24:25.813
Selling cosmetics.

24:27.972 --> 24:28.613
Thank you.

24:30.813 --> 24:31.893
Let's treat her to a meal.

24:36.732 --> 24:37.373
Okay.

24:38.452 --> 24:39.252
However,

24:39.893 --> 24:41.373
she's working at a mall now.

24:42.012 --> 24:43.212
She might get off work late.

24:45.012 --> 24:45.573
It's okay.

24:46.052 --> 24:46.573
Let her know

24:46.972 --> 24:49.052
I'll adjust to her schedule

24:49.413 --> 24:50.413
to show my sincerity.

24:51.772 --> 24:52.373
No problem.

24:53.052 --> 24:53.653
I'll tell her.

24:57.532 --> 24:58.292
Delicious.

25:10.452 --> 25:11.133
This way, please.

25:13.692 --> 25:15.093
So many koi fish here.

25:18.452 --> 25:19.692
Mind your words.

25:20.573 --> 25:21.133
Okay, okay.

25:29.252 --> 25:30.373
I've ordered some dishes.

25:30.692 --> 25:32.653
Let's see what else you'd like.

25:32.893 --> 25:34.212
I eat anything. Thank you.

25:35.532 --> 25:36.413
Any vegetable?

25:36.772 --> 25:38.373
Golden mushroom shreds,

25:38.492 --> 25:39.452
chrysanthemum moss,

25:39.732 --> 25:40.692
baby bok choy,

25:40.772 --> 25:41.692
braised shallots,

25:41.813 --> 25:42.933
red peppers in sauce,

25:43.093 --> 25:44.052
counterfeit dish,

25:44.093 --> 25:45.692
and our signature stir-fry.

25:51.972 --> 25:52.413
Cousin,

25:53.692 --> 25:54.452
what do you want?

25:56.813 --> 25:57.692
I... I...

25:57.853 --> 25:59.093
Anything will do.

25:59.373 --> 26:01.532
Well, any spinach?

26:02.373 --> 26:03.333
Sorry, miss.

26:03.573 --> 26:05.133
We don't have a fixed menu here.

26:05.452 --> 26:06.853
Our menu changes daily based on

26:06.893 --> 26:09.333
the freshest seasonal ingredients
available at the market.

26:10.052 --> 26:11.573
Therefore, you can only order dishes

26:11.772 --> 26:12.292
on the menu.

26:14.212 --> 26:14.813
How about...?

26:16.173 --> 26:17.732
She prefers spinach.

26:18.373 --> 26:19.093
Go get some.

26:19.452 --> 26:19.853
Thank you.

26:20.012 --> 26:20.573
Yes, Mr. Shen.

26:21.093 --> 26:21.732
Thank you.

26:22.212 --> 26:22.933
Welcome.

26:23.212 --> 26:23.532
Here.

26:24.613 --> 26:24.933
Here.

26:25.452 --> 26:26.292
Welcome to Jingzhou.

26:26.532 --> 26:27.012
Thank you.

26:33.772 --> 26:35.492
Are you settling in well here?

26:35.933 --> 26:36.492
Very well.

26:36.853 --> 26:38.173
Both the food and accommodations.

26:39.012 --> 26:41.173
If you need any help,

26:41.413 --> 26:42.093
tell me anytime.

26:42.692 --> 26:43.813
I should be able to help.

26:44.373 --> 26:45.093
No need.

26:45.292 --> 26:46.012
Yan has been

26:46.052 --> 26:47.133
caring for me.

26:47.173 --> 26:47.933
My life now

26:47.972 --> 26:48.972
is back on track.

26:49.653 --> 26:50.452
Yan told me

26:50.492 --> 26:51.492
you're busy with work.

26:51.573 --> 26:52.972
Running such a large company,

26:53.173 --> 26:54.292
I shouldn't bother you.

26:54.573 --> 26:55.292
We're family.

26:55.613 --> 26:56.093
It's okay.

27:03.893 --> 27:05.133
You mentioned liking this dish,

27:05.813 --> 27:06.573
so I reserved it.

27:07.732 --> 27:08.853
I just mentioned it,

27:09.093 --> 27:10.093
yet you remembered.

27:10.452 --> 27:11.012
Try it?

27:11.133 --> 27:11.972
No, you have it.

27:12.532 --> 27:13.893
I'm glad to see you two like this.

27:14.373 --> 27:15.933
Yan always

27:16.173 --> 27:18.133
praises you to me,

27:18.292 --> 27:19.893
saying you treat her so well.

27:20.212 --> 27:21.732
Witnessing it with my own eyes today,

27:21.933 --> 27:22.653
it's wonderful.

27:28.853 --> 27:29.413
Thank you.

27:30.613 --> 27:31.093
Cousin,

27:31.532 --> 27:32.532
tell me more.

27:32.893 --> 27:34.173
What else did she say about me?

27:36.653 --> 27:37.893
She loves you deeply.

27:39.212 --> 27:40.893
Yan had always been top of her class.

27:41.133 --> 27:42.012
She studied hard,

27:42.173 --> 27:43.173
excelled in academic.

27:43.333 --> 27:44.093
And she's pretty.

27:44.373 --> 27:45.333
Back in school,

27:45.373 --> 27:46.212
she's a top student

27:46.252 --> 27:47.333
and the campus belle.

27:47.692 --> 27:49.333
Many boys wanted to pursue her.

27:49.893 --> 27:50.813
But Yan

27:50.853 --> 27:51.653
was only focused on

27:51.653 --> 27:52.413
her studies

27:52.452 --> 27:53.212
and ignored boys.

27:53.813 --> 27:54.772
I used to wonder,

27:54.813 --> 27:55.413
she is

27:55.492 --> 27:56.772
with such high standards,

27:56.893 --> 27:58.452
who could possibly win her heart?

27:59.052 --> 27:59.893
You're so lucky.

28:00.012 --> 28:01.252
You are her first love.

28:06.613 --> 28:07.373
Really.

28:07.613 --> 28:08.853
When we were in school,

28:09.012 --> 28:10.532
she had zero interest in dating.

28:10.692 --> 28:11.492
To her,

28:11.532 --> 28:12.732
boys basically didn't exist.

28:12.853 --> 28:14.133
If the town had a girls' school,

28:14.252 --> 28:15.813
she would've transferred there.

28:18.012 --> 28:18.853
Were you two

28:18.893 --> 28:19.893
studying together?

28:21.012 --> 28:22.532
I remember Yan told me

28:22.613 --> 28:25.413
your hometown is Jincheng, Shanxi.

28:36.133 --> 28:36.492
Well...

28:36.732 --> 28:37.413
Good memory!

28:39.452 --> 28:39.972
Yes.

28:40.333 --> 28:40.813
I...

28:42.173 --> 28:44.532
I wasn't good at studying.

28:44.573 --> 28:45.544
In high school,

28:45.544 --> 28:46.384
I repeated two grades

28:46.384 --> 28:47.212
and transferred to

28:47.252 --> 28:48.653
Yan's school

28:48.732 --> 28:50.732
for remedial classes.

28:50.772 --> 28:52.093
So we ended up studying together.

28:55.413 --> 28:55.813
Excuse me,

28:55.933 --> 28:56.653
allow me to serve.

28:58.692 --> 28:59.933
She's exactly the same.

29:00.012 --> 29:01.413
Back in school,

29:01.893 --> 29:03.373
she'd always interrupt the teachers.

29:03.573 --> 29:04.573
She still does it now.

29:05.492 --> 29:06.653
Try the spinach.

29:07.653 --> 29:08.093
Here.

29:08.373 --> 29:08.972
Don't be shy.

29:10.893 --> 29:11.732
We should

29:11.732 --> 29:12.573
meet up more often.

29:12.933 --> 29:14.012
I really enjoy hearing you

29:14.052 --> 29:15.012
talk about Yan's past.

29:15.292 --> 29:16.373
Sure, no problem.

29:19.173 --> 29:20.813
(Mind your words.)

29:20.972 --> 29:21.653
But I'm busy.

29:22.972 --> 29:23.972
You two just go dating.

29:24.093 --> 29:24.972
I'm glad that you two

29:25.012 --> 29:25.772
get along well.

29:28.813 --> 29:29.853
Here, have some more.

29:33.373 --> 29:34.173
Yan isn't the type

29:34.853 --> 29:36.133
to fall for anyone easily.

29:36.813 --> 29:38.173
But once she does,

29:38.933 --> 29:40.012
it's for a lifetime.

29:43.492 --> 29:44.772
You better cherish her, okay?

29:48.692 --> 29:49.373
Don't worry.

29:50.093 --> 29:50.653
I will.

29:51.813 --> 29:52.333
Good.

30:00.173 --> 30:00.613
Here.

30:09.853 --> 30:10.492
By the way,

30:10.933 --> 30:12.212
any plans after the meal?

30:15.933 --> 30:16.452
There is

30:16.933 --> 30:18.012
a Sky Lounge here

30:18.692 --> 30:19.893
where you can see

30:19.933 --> 30:21.653
the Jingzhou's night view.

30:22.012 --> 30:22.692
It's stunning.

30:22.893 --> 30:23.813
I take her there often.

30:24.373 --> 30:25.573
Why not mention it sooner?

30:25.732 --> 30:26.813
We made plans

30:26.853 --> 30:27.692
to go shopping.

30:29.933 --> 30:31.333
But the Sky Lounge is amazing.

30:31.613 --> 30:32.853
It's a must-see in Jingzhou.

30:33.492 --> 30:34.212
Another day?

30:35.413 --> 30:35.853
Sure.

30:36.853 --> 30:37.292
Next time.

30:40.093 --> 30:40.573
Excuse me.

30:45.093 --> 30:45.893
Eat raw food?

30:45.972 --> 30:46.853
Yes, okay.

30:46.893 --> 30:47.292
Eat it.

30:47.333 --> 30:47.972
Okay, thanks.

30:48.212 --> 30:48.573
Here.

30:49.012 --> 30:49.532
I'll do it.

30:49.772 --> 30:50.252
Alright.

30:50.333 --> 30:51.532
Thank you.

31:15.133 --> 31:16.613
You talked quite a lot today.

31:18.532 --> 31:19.413
Think I enjoy this?

31:19.813 --> 31:20.933
Just to let him know

31:20.972 --> 31:21.813
you love him deeply.

31:23.492 --> 31:24.093
Why?

31:25.933 --> 31:27.413
I consulted a lawyer.

31:27.692 --> 31:28.972
The lawyer said

31:29.373 --> 31:30.813
as long as your relationship

31:30.813 --> 31:31.573
is genuine,

31:31.813 --> 31:33.052
and the man believes

31:33.093 --> 31:33.813
you love him,

31:33.853 --> 31:35.012
while he loves you too,

31:35.413 --> 31:36.452
and then even if the truth

31:36.492 --> 31:37.692
comes out,

31:37.972 --> 31:38.893
as long as he chooses

31:38.933 --> 31:39.772
to stand by you,

31:39.813 --> 31:41.252
you won't be put in jail.

31:50.252 --> 31:51.492
Don't think this means

31:51.532 --> 31:52.893
I approve of what you're doing.

31:53.813 --> 31:54.373
Have any idea

31:54.413 --> 31:55.613
what I felt today

31:55.653 --> 31:58.093
hearing those dishes name?

31:58.492 --> 32:00.613
I felt so worried.

32:00.692 --> 32:01.532
So scary!

32:03.252 --> 32:04.732
You must've been scared too, right?

32:07.093 --> 32:08.012
Why that look?

32:11.813 --> 32:12.333
Nothing.

32:13.853 --> 32:14.972
I just want to say that

32:17.532 --> 32:19.093
you could join us for meals more often

32:19.772 --> 32:20.933
to upgrade your dining.

32:24.972 --> 32:26.732
Not afraid I'll reveal your secret

32:26.772 --> 32:27.933
and cause you trouble?

32:30.093 --> 32:31.653
It's okay. Not that bad.

32:33.212 --> 32:33.853
That works.

32:34.573 --> 32:36.173
Then I'll just keep brainwashing him,

32:36.452 --> 32:38.052
and reminding him how much you love him.

32:40.292 --> 32:41.052
No need.

32:43.093 --> 32:43.972
He can feel

32:44.012 --> 32:45.012
how much I love him.

32:45.772 --> 32:46.933
Don't be that confident.

32:47.573 --> 32:48.893
Men are oblivious.

32:49.052 --> 32:50.173
Think he understands,

32:50.373 --> 32:51.212
what if he

32:51.252 --> 32:52.413
feels nothing at all?

32:52.692 --> 32:53.853
Watched those TV commercials,

32:53.893 --> 32:54.452
didn't you?

32:54.653 --> 32:55.492
Remind him

32:55.653 --> 32:56.413
again and again.

32:56.452 --> 32:58.012
Even it means countless times.

32:58.012 --> 32:58.933
To let him remember

32:59.093 --> 33:00.093
how much you love him.

33:04.613 --> 33:05.653
I saw you smiling.

33:05.692 --> 33:06.492
What's funny?

33:10.052 --> 33:10.972
You're quite adorable.

33:11.333 --> 33:12.133
Talk less.

33:12.972 --> 33:14.333
Well, I know

33:14.373 --> 33:15.653
I'm adorable.

33:17.173 --> 33:18.292
But listen.

33:18.333 --> 33:19.692
You still need

33:19.732 --> 33:20.452
to talk it out

33:20.492 --> 33:21.613
to your husband, okay?

33:26.692 --> 33:27.732
Feels like we haven't

33:27.772 --> 33:29.133
walked like this in ages, right?

33:38.692 --> 33:39.532
Cool!

33:39.732 --> 33:41.452
Exactly. So cool!

33:57.692 --> 33:58.532
What are you seeing?

33:59.653 --> 34:00.492
Nothing.

34:00.772 --> 34:01.613
Let's go home.

34:08.452 --> 34:09.132
Qiao Yan.

34:12.012 --> 34:12.853
Take it.

34:14.612 --> 34:15.572
What's this about?

34:16.092 --> 34:16.853
Keep it.

34:17.572 --> 34:18.213
I don't want it.

34:18.733 --> 34:19.853
Just take it.

34:20.132 --> 34:21.532
You always came

34:21.612 --> 34:22.813
to see this thing,

34:23.012 --> 34:24.012
so I'll give you mine.

34:24.773 --> 34:25.532
What about you?

34:25.773 --> 34:27.413
My birthday is next month.

34:27.933 --> 34:29.012
I'll have my parents buy me

34:29.052 --> 34:29.972
a new MP4 player.

34:32.213 --> 34:33.492
Alright, try it.

34:33.933 --> 34:34.933
The sound is great.

34:44.853 --> 34:46.172
Can you hear it?

34:47.452 --> 34:48.532
No sound.

34:49.572 --> 34:50.532
Impossible.

34:54.452 --> 34:55.572
Can you hear it now?

34:59.012 --> 34:59.933
There are

35:00.092 --> 35:01.333
all my favorite songs in it.

35:02.572 --> 35:03.652
You can download

35:03.693 --> 35:04.853
your favorite songs.

35:04.972 --> 35:05.532
Okay.

35:06.333 --> 35:07.333
Do you like the music?

35:07.492 --> 35:08.092
It's good.

35:17.012 --> 35:17.813
The night view

35:17.813 --> 35:19.213
is truly stunning.

35:22.132 --> 35:23.652
Sky Lounge, right?

35:23.853 --> 35:25.012
When do you take me there?

35:26.293 --> 35:27.132
Anytime.

35:28.293 --> 35:29.293
Sky Lounge.

35:29.532 --> 35:31.213
I want to visit the museum,

35:31.652 --> 35:32.172
anime expos,

35:32.492 --> 35:33.733
water parks,

35:33.893 --> 35:34.532
and that

35:35.172 --> 35:35.693
aquarium.

35:42.213 --> 35:43.213
Ruyi!

35:43.293 --> 35:44.893
From now on, you're my horse.

35:45.132 --> 35:46.213
I'll take good care of you.

35:46.773 --> 35:47.253
Haochen.

35:49.733 --> 35:50.293
Haochen.

35:50.773 --> 35:51.612
Are you hot?

35:55.452 --> 35:57.132
Haoming had things to do,

35:57.373 --> 35:57.933
so I'm here.

35:59.092 --> 35:59.452
Look!

36:00.172 --> 36:00.773
This...

36:02.052 --> 36:02.813
The cooling spray.

36:02.893 --> 36:03.452
Feel cooler?

36:07.693 --> 36:09.012
Switched horses already?

36:09.413 --> 36:10.492
This horse is cool!

36:11.612 --> 36:12.612
Cooler than the last one.

36:13.253 --> 36:14.413
I just talked

36:14.452 --> 36:15.213
with your coach.

36:15.492 --> 36:16.132
He said

36:17.012 --> 36:18.253
after switching horses,

36:18.492 --> 36:19.373
take it slow

36:19.413 --> 36:20.333
and gradually adapt

36:20.733 --> 36:21.532
to the rhythm

36:21.572 --> 36:22.813
and movement.

36:23.172 --> 36:24.452
After you mount,

36:24.532 --> 36:25.293
be careful.

36:25.693 --> 36:26.652
And after that...

36:26.972 --> 36:27.693
Go away.

36:30.092 --> 36:30.693
Let's go.

36:31.092 --> 36:32.213
Be careful, Haochen.

37:25.733 --> 37:26.253
Haochen!

37:30.576 --> 37:33.904
(Jingzhou Yuekang Hospital)

37:34.813 --> 37:35.373
Haochen.

37:35.813 --> 37:36.452
This bone broth

37:36.492 --> 37:37.532
was simmered

37:37.572 --> 37:38.612
for three hours.

37:39.172 --> 37:40.293
It has Chinese herbs

37:40.373 --> 37:41.092
to help your leg

37:41.172 --> 37:42.293
recover soon.

37:42.813 --> 37:43.452
Look at you.

37:43.733 --> 37:45.213
Why were you so careless?

37:45.893 --> 37:47.213
It wasn't his fault,

37:47.492 --> 37:48.652
but that riding club's fault.

37:48.972 --> 37:49.452
Understood?

37:49.652 --> 37:50.452
The coaches' fault.

37:51.092 --> 37:52.293
I'll find you a better club.

37:52.373 --> 37:53.012
Their coaches

37:53.132 --> 37:54.572
are all former professional racers

37:54.652 --> 37:55.333
with medals.

37:56.773 --> 37:58.693
You injured seriously.

37:59.413 --> 38:00.972
Don't move around out of impatience.

38:01.293 --> 38:02.012
It'd be terrible

38:02.172 --> 38:03.333
if you don't recover, got it?

38:04.132 --> 38:04.773
Hear that?

38:04.813 --> 38:05.773
Mom, Dad.

38:06.492 --> 38:07.132
Caregiver.

38:07.253 --> 38:07.612
Good.

38:10.413 --> 38:11.293
Hello.

38:11.452 --> 38:12.132
I'm his mother.

38:12.492 --> 38:13.693
He has a fracture.

38:13.773 --> 38:14.972
Don't let him off his bed.

38:15.132 --> 38:16.413
We're counting on you.

38:16.733 --> 38:17.253
Trust me.

38:17.333 --> 38:18.052
Thank you.

38:18.172 --> 38:18.733
- Thank you.
- One last sip.

38:19.972 --> 38:20.532
Haochen.

38:20.893 --> 38:21.773
Dad and I

38:21.813 --> 38:23.172
have an engagement.

38:23.413 --> 38:24.492
We'll come tomorrow.

38:25.213 --> 38:25.813
We're leaving.

38:26.572 --> 38:27.893
Dinner with Shifeng's executives.

38:29.253 --> 38:29.652
Good boy.

38:31.132 --> 38:31.652
Yan.

38:31.733 --> 38:32.333
Thank you.

38:32.452 --> 38:33.012
Thank you.

38:33.052 --> 38:33.532
Okay.

38:35.893 --> 38:36.373
I'll do it.

38:36.452 --> 38:36.813
Here.

38:37.012 --> 38:38.092
Let me feed you, okay?

38:38.213 --> 38:38.773
Haoming.

38:44.933 --> 38:45.373
I need...

38:45.413 --> 38:46.213
I'm running late

38:46.452 --> 38:47.052
for a dinner.

38:49.333 --> 38:49.813
Talk later.

38:53.333 --> 38:54.333
Here, take a sip.

39:10.612 --> 39:11.813
Come on. Drink more.

39:12.172 --> 39:12.492
Here.

39:13.012 --> 39:13.333
Right.

39:13.733 --> 39:14.052
Good.

39:30.652 --> 39:31.333
No more drinking.

39:32.132 --> 39:32.813
No more?

39:33.293 --> 39:35.733
Then... how about some fruits?

39:36.052 --> 39:36.572
Okay?

39:36.933 --> 39:37.452
Look.

39:37.532 --> 39:38.733
Pick something you like.

39:38.972 --> 39:40.172
I don't eat fruits.

39:40.253 --> 39:40.572
This...

39:41.293 --> 39:41.773
What's up?

39:41.773 --> 39:42.452
No!

39:42.893 --> 39:44.132
Leave! I don't want you!

39:44.213 --> 39:45.092
Just say it.

39:45.132 --> 39:46.052
- Leave!
- Why hit me?

39:46.092 --> 39:46.612
Outrageous!

39:46.652 --> 39:47.092
What's up?

39:47.373 --> 39:47.693
No.

39:47.773 --> 39:49.012
Leave!

39:49.492 --> 39:51.373
Stop talking to me!

39:52.132 --> 39:52.773
Stop it!

39:52.816 --> 39:53.712
- Leave!
- I quit!

39:55.373 --> 39:55.972
I'm sorry.

39:56.092 --> 39:56.773
So sorry.

39:56.813 --> 39:57.253
I quit.

39:57.413 --> 39:58.452
What about more money?

39:58.492 --> 39:59.333
No way.

39:59.853 --> 40:01.052
Never seen a child like this.

40:01.532 --> 40:02.092
I can't do it.

40:35.213 --> 40:36.733
I don't want to see you. Leave!

40:39.172 --> 40:39.853
I refuse.

40:40.253 --> 40:40.652
You!

40:41.373 --> 40:41.652
You!

40:41.693 --> 40:42.293
Kick me out.

40:43.092 --> 40:43.733
Come down here.

40:45.652 --> 40:46.253
It hurts.

40:46.452 --> 40:47.052
Can't get down.

40:48.733 --> 40:49.532
Listen.

40:49.933 --> 40:50.652
You'll stay in bed

40:51.612 --> 40:52.933
for four weeks.

40:54.092 --> 40:55.092
Your parents

40:55.213 --> 40:55.693
and Haoming

40:56.532 --> 40:58.052
entrust you to me.

40:59.492 --> 41:00.693
During these four weeks,

41:01.773 --> 41:02.933
behave yourself.

41:04.052 --> 41:05.132
Otherwise,

41:06.853 --> 41:07.652
you'll suffer.

41:17.052 --> 41:17.652
Fine.

41:18.532 --> 41:20.092
If you stay here,

41:21.092 --> 41:22.253
get me some fruits.

41:25.293 --> 41:26.733
Take those leftover ones.

41:29.972 --> 41:30.413
I...

41:32.612 --> 41:34.012
I-I want water.

41:45.532 --> 41:48.172
Hurry up! I'm dying of thirst!

42:01.132 --> 42:02.293
It's too cold.

42:02.853 --> 42:03.733
I always drink

42:03.773 --> 42:04.933
warm water.

42:05.333 --> 42:06.333
Knock it off.

42:09.373 --> 42:10.172
This is a hospital.

42:11.373 --> 42:13.172
You don't know me.

42:14.492 --> 42:15.733
I-I need food.

42:31.213 --> 42:32.893
I can't reach the fruit.

42:32.933 --> 42:33.652
Feed me one.

42:33.933 --> 42:35.012
Feed me this meal too.

42:37.532 --> 42:38.373
Your hands are hurt?

42:39.773 --> 42:41.132
The doctor never said that.

42:41.813 --> 42:42.413
Eat it.

42:45.853 --> 42:46.853
When Haoming was here,

42:46.893 --> 42:47.853
you treated me well.

42:48.333 --> 42:49.492
Now that he's gone,

42:49.773 --> 42:50.733
you're bullying me?

42:50.773 --> 42:51.813
When Haoming was here,

42:51.853 --> 42:52.773
you were like an angel.

42:52.972 --> 42:54.693
Now that he's gone, you're bullying me?

42:55.612 --> 42:56.373
I'm injured.

42:56.413 --> 42:57.972
I-I'm a kid!

42:58.172 --> 42:59.012
If you bully me,

42:59.773 --> 43:01.293
my brother will punish you.

43:02.333 --> 43:02.813
Alright.

43:04.773 --> 43:05.360
Skip the meal.

43:08.853 --> 43:09.413
Stop it.

43:09.813 --> 43:11.492
What?

43:14.612 --> 43:15.253
What's wrong?

43:17.893 --> 43:18.733
I'll call the doctor.

43:18.773 --> 43:19.213
Wait.

43:19.612 --> 43:20.853
Hey,

43:20.972 --> 43:22.933
I need to pee.

43:23.293 --> 43:24.733
Just say it.

43:25.213 --> 43:26.172
Don't you see

43:26.213 --> 43:27.532
I'm clutching my stomach?

43:32.213 --> 43:32.773
Is this okay?

43:33.773 --> 43:34.213
I'll help.

43:34.572 --> 43:35.452
No! I'll do it myself.

43:39.893 --> 43:40.773
Watch me pee?

